      "review_summary": "The PR preserves plugin-authored tool availability on cached descriptors, adds registration-time console warnings for malformed empty or non-array groups, and adds descriptor-cache tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +94, Tests +280. Total +374 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows current main drops plugin-authored availability during descriptor capture while the evaluator returns unsupported-signal diagnostics for empty groups; the PR defect is source-reproducible with plugin availability like { kind: \"config\" } missing path.",
